---
title: Scotland's Cheesy Square Sausage Burger with Caramelised Onion and Rosemary Chips
description: "O Flower of Scotland!" Show your support this Six Nations with burgers inspired by each team's homeland! An homage to the Scottish Lorne sausage, this Cheesy Square Sausage Burger is best served pitch-side with caramelised onion and rosemary chips.
